name: Alien Autopsy Memories for Pen Addict Episode 600

content.html:
My Jonathon Brook’s Alien Autopsy, a double ender pen with grinds by Mark Bacas.

One end has an Architect paired with Luminous ink, and the other a Cursive Italic paired with Matador Red ink.

This pen marked going to the pen show to see my friends.

name: Spano – a minimum-viable Micropub Media Endpoint

summary.html: Micropub is an open API standard to create posts on one’s own domain using third-party clients  and currently a W3C Candidate Recommendation. One of the (semi-) recent additions is the idea of a Micropub Media Endpoint. The Media Endpoint provides a way for Micropub clients to upload media files…
